*.log
*.inspection.json

# Per-seed ReplayReport dumps and usage records are regenerable heavyweight scratch:
# TraceScalingAblation._report_sink writes exactly the *_seed<N>.json pattern, and every
# runner writes .usage.json next to its --out. Summaries/calibration JSONs stay tracked.
# Scoped to confidence/ — older studies' tracked .usage.json artifacts must stay re-addable
# (wmh/repo_layout_test.py forbids ignore rules matching tracked files).
confidence/**/*_seed*.json
confidence/**/*.usage.json
confidence/figs/*.png
